telemetry.event.game_load_times.title: Yóu-syì jyā-dzài shŕ-jyān
telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Lyǎu-jyě Minecraft de jěng-tǐ syìng-néng gài-kwàng, kě-yǐ bāng-jù wǒ-men jēn-dwèi gè-jǔng jī-syíng hé tsāu-dzwò-syì-tǔng tyáu-jěng yǔ yōu-hwà yóu-syì.
Yóu-syì bǎn-běn-syìn-syī yě bāu-hán dzài chí-jūng, yǐ bāng-jù wǒ-men bǐ-jyàu Minecraft syīn bǎn-běn de syìng-néng gài-kwàng.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: Dwèi wǒ-men ér-yán, lyǎu-jyě jyā-rù shr̀-jyè swǒ syū de shŕ-cháng, yǐ-jí jè-yī shŕ-cháng swéi-je shŕ-jyān-twēi-yí hwèi rú-hé byàn-hwà shr̀ hěn jùng-yàu de. bǐ-rú, dāng wǒ-men jyā-rù syīn gūng-néng hwò jìn-syíng jyàu-dà de jì-shù gēng-gǎi shŕ, wǒ-men syū-yàu jr̄-dàu jè dwèi jyā-dzài shŕ-jyān yǒu-hé yǐng-syǎng.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Shr̀-jyè jyā-dzài shŕ-jyān
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Lyǎu-jyě wán-jyā wán Minecraft shŕ de syì-jyé (lì-rú yóu-syì mwó-shr̀、kè-hù-dwān hwò fú-wù-dwān shr̀-fǒu bèi syōu-gǎi, yǐ-jí yóu-syì bǎn-běn) yǒu-jù-yú wǒ-men dzài yóu-syì gēng-syīn shŕ jù-jùng gǎi-jìn wán-jyā dzwèi gwān-syīn de bù-fen. 
Shr̀-jyè jyā-dzài shr̀-jyàn jyāng túng shr̀-jyè syè-dzài shr̀-jyàn yī-chǐ yùng-yú jì-swàn yóu-syì hwèi-hwà de chŕ-syù shŕ-cháng.

telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
Tsž shr̀-jyàn yǔ shr̀-jyè jyā-dzài shr̀-jyàn yùng-yú jì-swàn shr̀-jyè hwèi-hwà de chŕ-syù-shŕ-jyān. 
Chŕ-syù-shŕ-jyān (yǐ myǎu hé kè wéi dān-wèi) dzài shr̀-jyè hwèi-hwà jyé-shù shŕ (twèi-hwéi dàu byāu-tí píng-mù, hwò tsúng fú-wù-chì dwàn-kāi-lyán-jyē) tsè-lyáng.
